snippet.title: Viking Vengeance - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to Steam on April 8. Wishlist NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1082890/Viking_Vengeance/

Viking Vengeance is a God-Worshiping Rogue-lite Dungeon Crawler ARPG set in a historical fiction world. You play as a Templar with pagan origins who rediscovers his roots and learns to wield the powers of the Norse Gods in his quest to change the destiny of his people and stop Ragnarok.

https://vikingvengeancegame.com
https://discord.gg/vikingvengeance
https://twitter.com/lowpolyint
https://www.facebook.com/gaming/VikingVengeanceGame


Credited Voice Actors:
William Kucmierowski (Wotan): https://www.imdb.com/name/nm2620244/?ref_=tt_cl_t1
Tom Greer (Heimdallr): https://www.imdb.com/name/nm8692826/?ref_=tt_cl_t2
Nyla Laurie (Vanadis): https://www.imdb.com/name/nm12425832/?ref_=tt_cl_t3
Jimmy Dean (Emperor): https://www.imdb.com/name/nm12425833/?ref_=tt_cl_t4
Luca Xavier (Thor / Loki / Odin): https://www.imdb.com/name/nm12425831/?ref_=tt_cl_t5
